title: America’s Coolest Fencer Takes It To the Street
text:
0 comments 
This weekend, star fencer Miles Chamley-Watson will take his signature style to San Jose, CA for the Men’s Foil World Cup, with an opportunity to gain valuable points towards qualifying for Rio. Never one for convention, this 6’4 tattooed model shows how he trains through every step of his day in the streets of New York City where he lives.
